    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Choose a point you can see on the ground within range. A series of Steel pikes rocket upwards from the ground in a 15-foot cube. Each creature in that area must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 3d10 earth damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. If a creature fails this save by 5 or more they gain 2 ranks of bleeding.</p><p><strong>At Higher Rank:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 2d10.</p>",
